<title>
DTC P0796 / P0797
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A5504029001">
<title>
DTC Detecting Condition and Trouble Area
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.366in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.831in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Trouble area
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0796: Pressure Control Solenoid “C” Performance / Stuck Off
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Calculated ratio for planetary gear unit is more than specified value for specified time even if low brake solenoid is ON.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Low brake control solenoid valve and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
TCM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0797: Pressure Control Solenoid “C” Stuck On
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
This DTC is detected if any one of the following conditions is met.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
When actual ratio of planetary gear unit is out of specification, deceleration ratio is higher than specification.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Planetary gear unit does not change to the 2nd speed for specified time, even if low brake solenoid is OFF.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
