<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A5504029003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Perform road test in a place where there is no traffic to prevent an accident.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Road test should be performed with two persons, a driver and a tester, on a level road.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<topic id = "AENCP70A5504029004">
<title>
P0796
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
If other DTC than P0796 is newly detected during this “DTC Confirmation Procedure”, troubleshoot the newly detected DTC first.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check that the following conditions are satisfied in this procedure.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Other DTC is not detected.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
11 V &#60; Battery voltage &#60; 15 V
</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and drive vehicle in D range at 1st speed for 2 sec. or more from state of being stopped, depressing accelerator pedal fully.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A5504029005">
<title>
P0797
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
If other DTC than P0797 is newly detected during this “DTC Confirmation Procedure”, troubleshoot the newly detected DTC first.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check that the following conditions are satisfied in this procedure.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Other DTC is not detected.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
11 V &#60; Battery voltage &#60; 15 V
</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and drive vehicle in D range at 2nd speed for 2 sec. or more, depressing the accelerator pedal to 20 to 30%, and driving vehicle at a speed of 50 km/h (31 mile/h) or more.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Stop vehicle.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition OFF, and leave ignition OFF for 10 sec.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Repeat Step 1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
</topic>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A5504029006">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENCP70A5504029007">
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A5504029008">
<question>
Was “CVT System Check” performed?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A5504001">CVT System Check</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A5504029009">
<title>
Low brake control solenoid valve drive circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
With ignition OFF, disconnect “C142”, “C09” and “E19” connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to “C142”, “C09” and “E19” connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance of “A5” circuit: less than 1 Ω
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A5” circuit and ground: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A5” circuit terminal and other terminal at “C142” connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Voltage of “A5” circuit: approx. 0 V (when ignition is ON)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A5504029010">
<title>
Low brake control solenoid valve check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check resistance of low brake control solenoid valve. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506029"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 4.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace low brake control solenoid valve (CVT assembly). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506017"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A5504029011">
<title>
Low brake control solenoid valve drive circuit signal check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Connect “C142”, “C09” and “E19” connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Connect an oscilloscope between “A5” and ground, and then check low brake control solenoid valve drive circuit signals. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5504055"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace CVT assembly. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506017"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Substitute a known-good TCM and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
</servinfosub>
